ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 216, New Brunswick
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 216 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of NEW BRUNSWICK, with respect to the severe rainstorm that that occurred from January 12 to 14, 2018.
